d on JUnit5. There's a checkstyle concern with Java import groups, like static and javax. I want to make sure existing styles are still applied. Also, should I check if text blocks are disallowed or if there's a line length limit? I'll confirm that everything is under the limit.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_074c9862d6a66281016a285714e874819594193245da236086\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKFcxc0W0I2rAN-ghsDjU_hreIOiqSMlzYbtXSo4XL8uwPjUYLaGd-NrlLsQUt8UiQKa8tj1RjsBiltvAeUCXbtfgMKz4N9nZ1-HljOrJEEVz248c9EYWxacPY4SBFDcSRahWITOhtUQ2gRw3e9aLLNNjqicVObkNARqwQMbuyjPp6Hblt1pXDNPfP7yWU4YOHYVUc-P9xFoUNCt2uZkOtYEh_0Wra-mUWrjV_T23k464hxLFUSmsyUNfIkbIdqOoM59OS1QeDGy1Zf5U-ZwnGpiUz0oN5sOEKQGtG4go1K2iEcKWclNp-QsddpJnrbVw0_TJntzHrUWzp2uYMMu4GGzdhf0i7UosRn_9I266vF26BUTbkC-g2jWsy59CTia-mpXSuBCB3RnYfwDSDDnt9G98dJa80nvthojfAypXRfN55U1HEQR-2DQwRN2-hXD_1-eI8pcLbr2wqmfWfX44MaqILu_5QQ6-LpA8GMi-z7hWcD_1sSABQ8shT5H7ZwUJWYLbI_3LGP6LY2NRBuTS1GVF46nPn3SpGHoGoR7GZEkJl8pnGdH3vreZPORaLehn5MiAyJq_Y0kKtNN2LeYCxXboUl7yLQqTx0UJnmK7aZTRL6ngoxkbiKA1MjEHAmrCtrywdruUnB8bonzzvwYJ7ZIt2eOm_BZXCY3vlzKRPK53GHJm113nH8lyArn4O4jBSmBCpRhI6Z5bmSM3R9sJX6NsiSJd0wpTSeo3PlSyPyVY3LFZnDMpnJ5YEUMDbtrCkkM91SkAgrianSIBhS3_sf3Y_dcXdEgyE5CdkB-9MvvtyysgbgJA9_yBT4WHSKVjE9MyZ5Ah2zncF4GgMNzN3FWahZf43DhoZGOEOU0P9qwAzbcz0SSdBg3JoFXqI9Q5dzm5EUrQIBbmJVi5fUwU_JgZy5f5JU3d_EIEC5C05LRcuaio5NJj9Je9ls9p1wRBZ_wdd3I9Xqxz016pU0NbzTdOL5RKiCxk_gc_4UzB45GjrR94uiHd3dRNDF8O0gT0zq10l-xHmHhz__M2Wtj_qFQuPEdE206XkXXzYT_6VUR2Vt8UhW85AE4oeiGDnP07L98YaLH2zx0A-6P0kXCfJVQQSiq26JyjdBrD_POMz8CIzKr02P08uIPxYA_KGfl4jltbxXzBXNF0dCdGw85qKuztNrg-eyXF9U-dU3bmeel_onhrHgv9qwVX34Axr0pY1XJ1myU6bbqQ2-lfB3G7rA81HeGpc21YVEzbTLCfgcn86kPISIVMRRzTIwo1M1-wH69E7uQ4lLgN6M1dYguUhJ7BopGGPnKDyqEsry2gSPMiHCABvUczy_EDP4mJu1R0shfWmmvJdHLzAwVSPp22VTvDUnElbXgjXf3XR4__T4YjxQo3aDchFvTokKSEzBu8AcXmFbOnMz9WaWFeRQv6rns5sTkNa9nCcQQUpAxow4Q-mtlPt0bIVqZuKCR8oCUSlMMJueJ82cyVsA_rrDrXXiQPMrbnzctt7bXMvZArEu47ekS2r2PAee4po1odbqV9ojsfAiamSIqKuypUaYA3omW8